'''Data plan''' refers to data quotas from a [[telecommunication]]s or data hosting contract. Data plans are offered by [[internet service provider]]s. These include mobile data plans, offered on [[cellular network]]s, from cellular telephony companies, and those from conventional fixed [[land line]] links, amongst other forms of offered [[data communication]]s. Network data hosting servers also offer plans based on data served, such as for websites.


